tags.note: Each of the 3 stands is too close to wall to park a bike at both sides
I've marked these as stands for want of a better tag-- these are planter boxes with a bicycle logo on them indicating they can be used as bike parking.
Small shelter called a "Bikehangar" - it is necessary to apply to rent a space to use it at www.cyclehoop.rentals. Has "Cycle Waltham Forest" branding and Waltham Forest Council's logo on it
